INSERT INTO service_faqs (service_page_id, question, answer, faq_order) VALUES
  (860, 'How does motion-activated lighting improve home security in Pacific Palisades?', 'Motion-activated security lights deter potential intruders by illuminating dark areas around your home, making it difficult for anyone to approach your property undetected. In Pacific Palisades, where homes are often set back from the street and surrounded by landscaping, proper motion lighting is essential for protecting entry points, driveways, and perimeter areas. Shaffer Construction designs and installs systems tailored to your property''s layout, ensuring complete coverage without light waste.', 1),
  (860, 'Can I integrate motion-activated lights with my smart home system in Pacific Palisades?', 'Absolutely. Modern motion-activated lights integrate seamlessly with smart home systems like Apple HomeKit, Google Home, and Alexa, giving you remote control and scheduling flexibility. You can monitor activity, adjust brightness, and receive alerts from anywhere—perfect for Pacific Palisades homeowners who travel or manage multiple properties. Shaffer Construction handles the complete installation and programming to ensure your security lighting works flawlessly with your existing smart home setup.', 2),
  (860, 'What''s the best placement for motion-activated lights around my Pacific Palisades home?', 'Strategic placement is key to effective security lighting. We recommend installing motion lights at entry points (front and back doors), along driveways, at gates, and around pool areas—any location where unauthorized access could occur. For Pacific Palisades homes with hillside properties or extensive landscaping, we conduct a thorough site assessment to identify vulnerable areas and design a system that balances security with aesthetic appeal.', 3),
  (860, 'How energy-efficient are motion-activated security lights?', 'Motion-activated lights are highly energy-efficient because they only operate when movement is detected, significantly reducing your electricity consumption compared to lights that run all night. LED motion lights are the most efficient option, using 80% less energy than traditional fixtures while providing superior brightness and durability. Shaffer Construction installs quality LED systems that lower your utility bills while providing reliable, long-lasting security protection.', 4),
  (860, 'What''s involved in upgrading older Pacific Palisades homes with modern security lighting?', 'Many Pacific Palisades homes were built decades ago with outdated or inadequate lighting systems. We assess your current setup, determine if electrical upgrades are needed, and install modern motion-activated lights that meet current codes and your security needs. The process typically includes running new wiring, installing smart sensors, and programming the system—all completed efficiently with minimal disruption to your home. Contact us for a free estimate on your security lighting upgrade.', 5);
